31:22.689 --> 31:23.990
<i>YOU HAVE</i>
<i>A PRE‐PAID CALL</i>

31:23.990 --> 31:26.492
<i>FROM AN INMATE</i>
<i>AT THE COUNTY JAIL.</i>

31:26.492 --> 31:28.895
YES.

31:28.895 --> 31:30.130
DAVID.

31:30.130 --> 31:32.032
<i>JIM.</i>

31:32.032 --> 31:33.534
I'M STILL HERE.

