TO THAT BASTARD.

31:41.041 --> 31:42.709
THERE'S NO OTHER
WAY, JIM.

31:42.709 --> 31:44.010
WHAT, WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO GET ON MY KNEES

31:44.010 --> 31:45.646
