31:45.646 --> 31:47.581
DO YOU WANT TO GET OUT
OF THERE OR NOT?

31:47.581 --> 31:48.915
YES, I DO.

31:48.915 --> 31:51.451
THEN YOU NEED TO APOLOGIZE.

31:51.451 --> 31:53.419
OKAY, I WILL.

31:53.419 --> 31:54.487
<i>YOU HAVE HIS NUMBER?</i>

31:54.487 --> 31:56.156
YES, I'VE GOT HIS NUMBER.
I'LL CALL HIM.

31:56.156 --> 31:59.259
OKAY, I'LL BE EXPECTING
A PRE‐PAID CALL FROM YOU.

31:59.259 --> 32:00.761
<i>OKAY, FINE.</i>

32:00.761 --> 32:02.569
ALL RIGHT. THE ‐‐
THE SOONER YOU GET ON THIS,

32:02.569 --> 32:04.404
THE SOONER YOU'LL
BE OUT OF THERE.

32:04.404 --> 32:06.873
LISTEN, I NEED YOU TO GET
SOMEBODY ELSE OUT OF HERE.

32:06.873 --> 32:08.809
<i>WHO?</i>

32:08.809 --> 32:11.044
WARRICK MENSEY LEWIS.

32:12.613 --> 32:13.614
WHO'S THAT?

32:13.614 --> 32:14.615
HE'S AN ALLY.

32:14.615 --> 32:15.849
AND I NEED TO GET HIM OUT.

32:15.849 --> 32:17.851
<i>WHAT'S HE IN FOR?</i>

32:17.851 --> 32:20.621
DRUG POSSESSION.

32:20.621 --> 32:22.088
JIM.

32:22.088 --> 32:24.257
DAVID, LISTEN,
I NEED TO GET HIM OUT.

32:24.257 --> 32:27.327
ALL RIGHT?
I DON'T WANT TO EXPLAIN MYSELF.

32:27.327 --> 32:31.031
FINE. I'LL GET WALLY ON IT.

32:31.031 --> 32:33.166
THANK YOU.

32:33.166 --> 32:35.335
LET ME KNOW AS SOON
AS YOU TALK TO JUDGE HAWTHORN.

32:35.335 --> 32:36.703
AND I'LL GET DOWN THERE
AND PICK YOU UP.

32:36.703 --> 32:38.104
YEAH.

32:38.104 --> 32:39.773
WILL DO.

32:44.911 --> 32:46.713
BUSY MAN.

32:46.713 --> 32:48.982
YES, SORRY.

32:48.982 --> 32:50.617
A LOT GOING ON.

32:50.617 --> 32:52.986
YEAH, I'M SURE.

32:52.986 --> 32:55.455
BUT NOW IT IS
JUST YOU AND ME.

32:55.455 --> 32:58.992
MM. UNTIL YOUR PHONE
RINGS AGAIN.

32:58.992 --> 33:00.567
I APOLOGIZE, IT'S...

33:00.567 --> 33:02.903
NO, IT'S FINE.

33:02.903 --> 33:05.572
I KIND OF LIKE IT.

33:05.572 --> 33:09.643
I MEAN, HERE YOU ARE, BUSY,
IMPORTANT MAN

33:09.643 --> 33:15.181
AND TALKING TO THE FUTURE LEADER
OF THE FREE WORLD?

33:15.181 --> 33:17.083
AND YET, HERE WE ARE.

33:17.083 --> 33:18.384
YES.

33:19.419 --> 33:20.453
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:22.288 --> 33:23.489
YEAH.

34:01.167 --> 34:02.969
KATHERYN, YOU'VE BEEN
SITTING THERE

34:02.969 --> 34:04.304
A WHILE WITH THE...

34:04.304 --> 34:07.207
YOU KNOW I CAN BE RUTHLESS.

34:07.207 --> 34:09.843
YOU KNOW I CAN BE CUNNING.

34:09.843 --> 34:12.112
YES.

34:12.112 --> 34:13.614
DID YOU FORGET?

34:17.884 --> 34:20.654
NO.

34:20.654 --> 34:22.923
WELL, YOU SURE AS HELL
WON'T FORGET NOW.

34:25.291 --> 34:28.929
YOU STOOD THERE
FOR A WHILE.

34:28.929 --> 34:30.964
YES.

34:30.964 --> 34:33.634
ARE YOU SHOCKED?

34:33.634 --> 34:36.436
YES.

34:36.436 --> 34:39.973
YOU SHOULD'VE HAD SOME TEA.

34:39.973 --> 34:44.845
I, UH, I HAVE
A DINNER PARTY TO ATTEND.

34:44.845 --> 34:47.180
AND I DIDN'T WANT TO
LOSE MY APPETITE.

34:47.180 --> 34:49.783
WHY DID YOU DO THAT?

34:49.783 --> 34:50.984
DO WHAT?

34:52.819 --> 34:55.556
ARE WE REALLY GONNA CONTINUE
PLAYING THIS GAME?

34:55.556 --> 34:57.323
HMM? IT'S JUST GONNA
DRIVE ME FURTHER

34:57.323 --> 34:59.125
INTO THIS INSANITY.

34:59.125 --> 35:01.301
HM?

35:01.301 --> 35:02.969
BUT THAT'S
A NICE DEFENSE, RIGHT?

35:02.969 --> 35:04.671
INSANITY?

35:04.671 --> 35:08.108
DON'T YOU THINK
THAT'S A NICE DEFENSE?

35:08.108 --> 35:11.912
YES, THAT WOULD BE
APPROPRIATE.

35:11.912 --> 35:14.214
WHY DID YOU DO
THAT TO MY SON?

35:15.516 --> 35:17.450
I ‐‐ I DIDN'T MEAN
FOR THAT TO HAPPEN.

35:17.450 --> 35:19.319
IS THAT RIGHT?

35:21.922 --> 35:24.424
NO, UH...

35:24.424 --> 35:26.226
OKAY.

35:26.226 --> 35:28.228
SO HOW DID YOU KNOW
HE WAS IN JAIL?

35:32.298 --> 35:33.667
HOW?!

35:38.338 --> 35:43.076
I, UH, I HAVE CLIENTS
FROM ALL WALKS OF LIFE.

35:45.278 --> 35:48.448
I HAVE MANY SOURCES.

35:48.448 --> 35:51.585
SO TELL ME ABOUT THE GUY
THAT WAS IN THE CELL WITH HIM.

35:55.488 --> 35:56.990
HE WAS MURDERED
IN HIS CELL.

35:56.990 --> 35:59.593
SO I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU WANT TO KNOW ABOUT THAT.

35:59.593 --> 36:04.337
I ASKED YOU
TO TELL ME ABOUT <i>HIM.</i>

36:04.337 --> 36:05.338
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO KNOW?

36:05.338 --> 36:07.674
WHAT WAS HIS NAME?

36:09.810 --> 36:12.012
UM...MILTON...

36:14.881 --> 36:17.984
WILTOS.

36:17.984 --> 36:20.186
AND WHAT WAS HE IN FOR?

36:20.186 --> 36:22.989
MURDER.
NOT RAPE?

36:22.989 --> 36:24.324
YES.

36:24.324 --> 36:28.228
DID YOU PUT HIM
IN THE CELL WITH MY SON?

36:28.228 --> 36:31.998
AND YOU DIDN'T THINK THAT WYATT
WOULD BE ASSAULTED BY HIM?

36:31.998 --> 36:33.066
NO, I THOUGHT...

36:33.066 --> 36:38.772
WERE YOU REALLY THINKING
ANYTHING AT ALL?

36:38.772 --> 36:41.975
MY SON WAS ASSAULTED
AS A CHILD, VERONICA.

36:41.975 --> 36:43.476
AND YOU KNEW THAT.

36:43.476 --> 36:46.880
KATHERYN, HE WASN'T
SUPPOSED TO GO THAT FAR!

36:46.880 --> 36:48.749
ALL I KNOW IS THAT
WE HAD TO SCARE HIM.

36:48.749 --> 36:51.051
AND JIM HAD HIM
TOO PROTECTED IN THERE.

36:51.051 --> 36:52.485
HE WASN'T SCARED!

36:52.485 --> 36:54.054
HE WAS SCARED, VERONICA.

36:54.054 --> 36:55.656
I SAW HIM.

36:55.656 --> 36:57.758
WELL, WHEN I SAW HIM
AT THIS HOUSE,

36:57.758 --> 36:59.626
HE WAS NOT SCARED.

36:59.626 --> 37:00.927
HE WAS GOING TO THE D. A.

37:00.927 --> 37:03.202
AND I JUST WANTED HIM
NOT TO DO THAT.

37:03.202 --> 37:05.038
SO I WANTED HIM
TO BE SCARED!

37:05.038 --> 37:07.073
AS A PARENT, I KNOW
WHEN A CHILD IS SCARED.

37:07.073 --> 37:08.675
AND THAT CHILD
WAS NOT SCARED.

37:08.675 --> 37:10.343
SO YOU'RE SAYING
I'M A BAD PARENT?

37:10.343 --> 37:11.811
NO, THAT'S NOT WHAT
I'M SAYING!

37:11.811 --> 37:13.046
THEN WHAT ARE YOU SAYING,
PLEASE?

37:13.046 --> 37:15.014
...PLEASE MAKE IT CLEAR
IF YOU DON'T MIND.

37:15.014 --> 37:16.783
I'M SAYING ‐‐

37:19.219 --> 37:22.723
I'M SAYING THAT HE NEEDED
TO BE FRIGHTENED.

37:22.723 --> 37:25.325
AND JIM WASN'T DOING THAT.

37:25.325 --> 37:28.662
HE NEEDED TO SEE WHAT IT WAS
REALLY LIKE IN THERE.

37:28.662 --> 37:30.831
THAT WAS
THE ONLY WAY, KATHERYN.

37:32.933 --> 37:36.202
AND HOW DID
YOUR PLAN WORK OUT?

37:40.040 --> 37:42.709
I LOVED WYATT.

37:42.709 --> 37:44.845
I LOVED WYATT.

37:44.845 --> 37:48.148
I WOULD NEVER DO ANYTHING
TO HURT HIM INTENTIONALLY.

37:48.148 --> 37:52.485
HOW DID IT WORK OUT?

37:57.190 --> 38:00.734
NOT GOOD.

38:00.734 --> 38:02.335
NOT GOOD AT ALL.

38:02.335 --> 38:04.337
NO.

38:04.337 --> 38:09.342
NOT GOOD FOR WYATT,
AND NOT GOOD FOR YOU AT ALL.

38:10.977 --> 38:13.079
WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

38:13.079 --> 38:14.981
DO YOU KNOW HOW WELL
I KNOW YOU?

38:19.553 --> 38:22.088
SURE.

38:22.088 --> 38:25.792
HMM. NO, I DON'T THINK
YOU DO.

38:25.792 --> 38:28.228
YOU ‐‐ I ‐‐ I KNOW
YOU KNOW ME, KATHERYN.

38:28.228 --> 38:29.763
I KNOW WHEN YOU'RE LYING.

38:29.763 --> 38:32.766
AND I KNOW WHEN YOU'RE
TELLING THE TRUTH.

38:32.766 --> 38:35.268
I KNOW YOU CAN BE RUTHLESS.

38:35.268 --> 38:39.640
AND I KNOW HOW DESPERATE
YOU ARE RIGHT ABOUT NOW.

38:39.640 --> 38:42.042
I'M SORRY, KATHERYN.

38:42.042 --> 38:45.345
YES, OF COURSE YOU ARE.

38:48.048 --> 38:50.517
LET ME SHOW YOU
HOW SORRY I AM.

38:50.517 --> 38:52.252
NOW, LET ME FIX THIS.

38:52.252 --> 38:56.623
YOU ARE MY FRIEND.
LET ME DO THIS FOR YOU.

38:56.623 --> 38:58.959
YES.

38:58.959 --> 39:01.602
FRIEND.

39:01.602 --> 39:06.907
MY FRIEND, WHO I KNOW
A LOT ABOUT.

39:06.907 --> 39:09.810
YOU'RE VERONICA HARRINGTON.

39:09.810 --> 39:13.547
LITTLE BROKE GIRL
FROM NEWCHESTER PROJECTS.

39:13.547 --> 39:16.683
YOUR MOTHER WAS A WHORE.

39:16.683 --> 39:18.284
AND YOUR FATHER?

39:18.284 --> 39:20.587
HE PLAYED THE NUMBERS
AND THE WOMEN.

39:20.587 --> 39:23.590
HE AND JIM HAVE THAT
IN COMMON.

39:23.590 --> 39:27.926
YOU'RE ONE OF FIVE CHILDREN,
ALL WHO HATE YOUR GUTS.

39:29.830 --> 39:32.198
YOU WERE SMART IN COLLEGE.

39:32.198 --> 39:36.269
BUT YOU NEEDED TO GET
THAT SCHOLARSHIP FROM MY FATHER.

39:36.269 --> 39:40.240
WE ALL KNOW WHAT YOU HAD
TO DO TO GET THAT.

39:40.240 --> 39:42.976
THAT MUST'VE BEEN DISGUSTING.

39:42.976 --> 39:45.812
HE WAS OLD AND WRINKLED
BY THAT POINT.

39:47.413 --> 39:51.351
ON PAPER, YOU'RE WORTH
ABOUT $25 MILLION.

39:51.351 --> 39:53.386
BUT YOU'VE GOT MORTGAGES
ON THOSE FACILITIES

39:53.386 --> 39:56.489
FOR MORE THAN $29 MILLION.

39:56.489 --> 40:01.201
SO TECHNICALLY, THAT MAKES YOU
NEGATIVE IN YOUR WORTH.

40:01.201 --> 40:02.468
YOU'RE MAKING PAYMENTS.

40:02.468 --> 40:04.404
BUT IF YOU DON'T GET
SOMEBODY IN THERE FAST,

40:04.404 --> 40:08.775
