THEY WILL SURVIVE.

40:08.775 --> 40:11.612
AND YOU'RE IN DEBT
WITH THE BANK.

40:12.445 --> 40:15.816
LLOYD BOWMAN
IS A DEAR FRIEND OF MINE.

40:15.816 --> 40:18.484
AND I'M ON THE BOARD
OF THAT BANK.

40:18.484 --> 40:20.386
I HAVE POWER.

40:21.888 --> 40:25.391
NOW ALL I WANT FROM YOU IS FOR
YOU TO...WITH ME.

40:25.391 --> 40:28.028
PLEASE.

40:28.028 --> 40:30.296
AND THE LIFE YOU THINK
YOU KNEW WILL BE OVER

40:30.296 --> 40:34.267
BEFORE YOU CAN SAY,
"KATHERYN."

40:34.267 --> 40:35.769
KATHERYN,
I WON'T DO ANYTHING.

40:35.769 --> 40:36.837
GET OUT OF THIS HOUSE.

40:36.837 --> 40:37.871
KATHERYN.

40:37.871 --> 40:39.172
OR STAY AND JOIN
JENNIFER ON THE FLOOR.

40:39.172 --> 40:40.206
BUT THE DOORS ARE LOCKED!

40:40.206 --> 40:41.975
OKAY.
BUT WHERE ARE THE KEYS?

40:41.975 --> 40:44.711
THE WINDOW ISN'T LOCKED.

40:44.711 --> 40:46.747
YOU WANT ME TO CLIMB
OUT OF THE WINDOW?

40:46.747 --> 40:49.650
