I WANT FROM YOU.

40:49.650 --> 40:51.417
BY THE TIME YOU PAY PENANCE

40:51.417 --> 40:54.054
FOR WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO MY SON,

40:54.054 --> 40:56.690
I AM NOT SURE
YOU WILL FULLY

40:56.690 --> 40:59.492
APPRECIATE THE GRAVE MISTAKE

40:59.492 --> 41:02.969
YOU MADE IN PUTTING THAT ANIMAL
IN THE CELL WITH MY SON.

41:02.969 --> 41:04.805
KATHERYN, I'M SORRY!

41:04.805 --> 41:06.673
I'M SORRY!

41:06.673 --> 41:08.041
AS A MATTER OF FACT...

41:09.610 --> 41:11.244
YOU NEED TO DIE, TOO.

41:11.244 --> 41:13.580
KATHERYN, STOP IT.
KATHERYN.

41:13.580 --> 41:14.848
KATHERYN, STOP IT NOW!

41:14.848 --> 41:16.517
