STOP IT!

41:16.517 --> 41:17.718
JUST PUT THE KNIFE DOWN!

41:17.718 --> 41:19.452
THIS?
YES!

41:19.452 --> 41:20.453
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

41:20.453 --> 41:22.088
KATHERYN! STOP IT!

41:22.088 --> 41:23.223
KATHERYN, DON'T MAKE ME STOP.

41:23.223 --> 41:25.058
DON'T MAKE ME!
DON'T MAKE YOU DO WHAT?

41:25.058 --> 41:27.293
[ SCREAMS ]

41:27.293 --> 41:29.495
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

