IN MY CAR.

41:46.847 --> 41:48.214
OF COURSE SHE PUT DRUGS
IN YOUR CAR.

41:48.214 --> 41:49.249
DON'T BE AN IDIOT.

41:49.249 --> 41:50.917
I THINK IT'S DISGUSTING,
YOU BEING GAY.

41:50.917 --> 41:52.118
YOU'RE GONNA PAY.

41:52.118 --> 41:53.787
